msgid "Scenario I: Return to The Untamed Wilds"
msgstr "冒险I：重返荒莽密林"

msgid "Remove the other 4 [[Jungle]] locations from the game. Do not include any of the other encounter cards listed in the original setup instructions (There should be a total of 5 cards.)"
msgstr "将其他4个[[丛林]]地点从游戏中移除，不要查看。不要加入原版的冒险设置指示中列出的其他遭遇卡。(卡牌总数应为5张。)"

msgid "The 'check your supplies' ability on the Expedition Camp can be used from any location."
msgstr "探险营地的‘查看你的补给品’能力可以在任意地点使用。"
